description: This top 15% Parvati purrs with a rating of 25, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 125, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 3 for East, 2 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
